        <briefdescription>
<para>Registers an object as the handler for a specific command type. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The handler object must provide a method: `bool submit(const CommandType&amp;) noexcept`. Upon registration, a static lambda (trampoline) is generated to handle type erasure and casting.</para>
